item.title: Save the cheerleader, save the world
item.author: Felix Editor,Srishti Bhasin,
item.description: Imperial College Titans are the university’s cheerleading team. The club is entering its 6th year of competition, with silver medals under our belt from last year’s nationals, and we need your support to go for gold. Cheerleading is one of the fastest growing sports in the UK, combining stunts, …
